# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:13
translate portuguese suzy1_b52dca5a:

    # "I go to the kitchen and make a plate with what's left, then sit down across from her at the table."
    "Vou à cozinha e preparo um prato com o que sobrou, depois sento-me à mesa, à frente dela."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:14
translate portuguese suzy1_c4e96a72:

    # "She puts her phone away and looks up at me."
    "Ela guarda o telemóvel e olha para mim."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:17
translate portuguese suzy1_43f2e75d:

    # ss "So how's it been going [bro]?"
    ss "Então, como é que tem corrido [bro]?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:18
translate portuguese suzy1_d48b3188:

    # pc "Pretty good, I guess."
    pc "Bastante bem, acho eu."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:19
translate portuguese suzy1_c84b49b4:

    # ss "Have you found out anything about Dad?"
    ss "Descobriste alguma coisa sobre o pai?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:20
translate portuguese suzy1_0b7558fc:

    # pc "Not yet."
    pc "Ainda não."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:22
translate portuguese suzy1_e47fa0f8:

    # ss "I miss him."
    ss "Tenho saudades dele."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:23
translate portuguese suzy1_0b941cef:

    # pc "You got along with him well?"
    pc "Davas-te bem com ele?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:24
translate portuguese suzy1_0442c0e0:

    # ss "Yeah."
    ss "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:25
translate portuguese suzy1_d244b907:

    # ss "I mean, we didn't spend a lot of time together. He was down in that basement a lot."
    ss "Quer dizer, não passávamos muito tempo juntos. Ele passava muito tempo naquela cave."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:26
translate portuguese suzy1_34edb007:

    # ss "But he would have breakfast with me every morning before school. He was funny. He'd make me laugh every day."
    ss "Mas tomava o pequeno-almoço comigo todas as manhãs antes da escola. Era engraçado. Fazia-me rir todos os dias."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:27
translate portuguese suzy1_85af114e:

    # pc "Kind of like this, huh?"
    pc "Mais ou menos assim, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:29
translate portuguese suzy1_226f4904:

    # ss "I said he was funny, not obnoxious. Plus, he wore pants. Why are you walking around in your boxers?"
    ss "Eu disse que ele era engraçado, não irritante. Além disso, ele usava calças. Porque é que andas por aí de boxers?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:30
translate portuguese suzy1_4cc016bf:

    # pc "It's morning, I don't want to get dressed yet. You can eat breakfast in your underwear if you want."
    pc "É de manhã, ainda não me apetece vestir-me. Podes tomar o pequeno-almoço de cueca, se quiseres."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:31
translate portuguese suzy1_bd01965a:

    # ss "Yeah, I bet you'd like that. You'd just stare at me the whole time."
    ss "Sim, aposto que gostarias disso. Ficarias só a olhar para mim o tempo todo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:35
translate portuguese suzy1_d7a0aba4:

    # ss "You're such a perv."
    ss "És mesmo um pervertido."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:38
translate portuguese suzy1_0ca3339d:

    # ss "You're such a jerk."
    ss "És mesmo um idiota."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:39
translate portuguese suzy1_a976ce63:

    # pc "Besides, you act like you don't stare at me when I'm in my boxers."
    pc "Além disso, fazes como se não ficasses a olhar para mim quando estou de cuecas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:40
translate portuguese suzy1_23992985:

    # ss "What!? I do not!"
    ss "O quê!? Não fico!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:41
translate portuguese suzy1_25e7a80f:

    # pc "Come on now [sis], I've seen you."
    pc "Vá lá [sis], já te vi."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:43
translate portuguese suzy1_873662ce:

    # ss "You're out of your mind. I've never stared at you. Like you have anything to stare at anyways."
    ss "Estás louco. Nunca fiquei a olhar para ti. Como se tivesses alguma coisa para olhar, de qualquer forma."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:44
translate portuguese suzy1_6e7bc529:

    # pc "Oh I don't have anything to stare at?"
    pc "Ah, não tenho nada para olhar?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:45
translate portuguese suzy1_ec7a8238:

    # ss "Nope."
    ss "Não."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:48
translate portuguese suzy1_7745b76d:

    # ss "Yeah, whatever."
    ss "Sim, tanto faz."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:51
translate portuguese suzy1_24166e5d:

    # ss "No! I don't want to see!"
    ss "Não! Não quero ver!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:52
translate portuguese suzy1_483160a9:

    # ss "Sit down. Stop playing around."
    ss "Senta-te. Pára de brincar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:53
translate portuguese suzy1_ce7899d2:

    # pc "I'm not playing. I'll show you."
    pc "Não estou a brincar. Vou mostrar-te."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:54
translate portuguese suzy1_626bbd17:

    # ss "I don't want to see it. I believe you have something there, but I don't want to see it."
    ss "Não quero ver. Acredito que tens algo aí, mas não quero ver."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:55
translate portuguese suzy1_c1226f21:

    # ss "Put it away, sit down."
    ss "Guarda isso, senta-te."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:56
translate portuguese suzy1_02b8ec2b:

    # pc "Alright, I'm sitting."
    pc "Tudo bem, vou sentar-me."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:58
translate portuguese suzy1_c7580a8a:

    # ss "You're such a weirdo."
    ss "És tão esquisita."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:59
translate portuguese suzy1_086a625f:

    # "We spend the rest of the breakfast talking about school and work and joking around."
    "Passamos o resto do pequeno-almoço a falar sobre a escola e o trabalho e a brincar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:60
translate portuguese suzy1_74d7aff9:

    # "Then we finish eating and it's time to go to school."
    "Depois terminamos de comer e está na hora de ir para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:65
translate portuguese suzy1_74b357a7:

    # ss "Have a good day [bro]. See you later."
    ss "Tem um bom dia [bro]. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:66
translate portuguese suzy1_7dee10c4:

    # pc "Bye [sis]."
    pc "Adeus [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy1.rpy:71
translate portuguese suzy1_015cad61:

    # "She leaves for school and I follow right after her."
    "Ela sai para a escola e eu sigo logo atrás dela."

